sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant Gateway as KServe Gateway<br/>(data-science-gateway)<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant RBAC as kube-rbac-proxy<br/>(RHOAI 3.x)
    participant REST as MLServer REST Server<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    participant GRPC as MLServer gRPC Server<br/>8081/TCP gRPC/HTTP2
    participant DP as DataPlane Handler
    participant Runtime as Model Runtime<br/>(sklearn/xgboost/lightgbm/onnx)
    participant Metrics as Metrics Server<br/>8082/TCP HTTP
    participant Prom as Prometheus
    participant OTel as OpenTelemetry Collector<br/>(optional)

    Note over Client,Runtime: Flow 1: REST Inference Request
    Client->>Gateway: POST /v2/models/{model}/infer<br/>HTTPS/443, TLS 1.2+
    Gateway->>RBAC: Auth check<br/>kube-rbac-proxy
    RBAC->>REST: HTTP/8080<br/>plaintext (in-pod)
    REST->>DP: Python call<br/>in-process
    DP->>Runtime: predict()<br/>in-process
    Runtime-->>DP: Prediction result
    DP-->>REST: InferenceResponse
    REST-->>Gateway: HTTP 200<br/>JSON Response
    Gateway-->>Client: HTTPS Response

    Note over Client,Runtime: Flow 2: gRPC Inference Request
    Client->>Gateway: ModelInfer RPC<br/>HTTPS/443, TLS 1.2+
    Gateway->>RBAC: Auth check
    RBAC->>GRPC: gRPC/HTTP2/8081<br/>plaintext (in-pod)
    GRPC->>DP: Python call<br/>in-process
    DP->>Runtime: predict()<br/>in-process
    Runtime-->>DP: Prediction result
    DP-->>GRPC: ModelInferResponse
    GRPC-->>Gateway: gRPC Response
    Gateway-->>Client: gRPC Response

    Note over Prom,Metrics: Flow 3: Prometheus Metrics Scrape
    Prom->>Metrics: GET /metrics<br/>HTTP/8082 plaintext
    Metrics-->>Prom: Prometheus metrics

    Note over REST,OTel: Flow 4: OpenTelemetry Tracing (Optional)
    REST->>OTel: OTLP traces<br/>gRPC (insecure)
    GRPC->>OTel: OTLP traces<br/>gRPC (insecure)
